                                                            channels and devices
                                                                                                                                                                                













Online
                                                                            
                                                                            
                                                                                
                                                                                


                                                                            Invest online and complete mutual fund transactions in a few simple clicks. 
                                                                        
                                                                        
                                                                        
                                                                            
                                                                            











Mobile
                                                                            
                                                                            
                                                                                
                                                                                


                                                                            Invest, earn returns and plan for your dreams, anytime, anywhere, with the SBI MF mobile app.
                                                                        
                                                                        
                                                                        
                                                                            
                                                                            













Offline
                                                                            
                                                                            
                                                                                
                                                                                


